{"content": "I need to multiply 37a \u00d7 635 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 37a (base 11) to base 10**\n- 37a\u2081\u2081 = 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 7\u00d711\u00b9 + 10\u00d711\u2070\n- = 3\u00d7121 + 7\u00d711 + 10\u00d71\n- = 363 + 77 + 10\n- = 450\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 635 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 635\u2081\u2081 = 6\u00d711\u00b2 + 3\u00d711\u00b9 + 5\u00d711\u2070\n- = 6\u00d7121 + 3\u00d711 + 5\u00d71\n- = 726 + 33 + 5\n- = 764\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 450 \u00d7 764 = 343,800\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 343,800 back to base 11**\n- 343,800 \u00f7 11 = 31,254 R 6\n- 31,254 \u00f7 11 = 2,841 R 3\n- 2,841 \u00f7 11 = 258 R 3\n- 258 \u00f7 11 = 23 R 5\n- 23 \u00f7 11 = 2 R 1\n- 2 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 215336\n\n**Answer: 215336**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 397}